
Ranger Help for: enemy amphibian
================================

SUMMARY:
Choosing amphibian means your Ranger has studied and learned to hate
frogfolk, toads, salamanders, and similar wet-skinned creatures that live
between water and land.

This is usually a strong thematic choice for swamp, beach, and other damp
territories. Expect it to matter most where marshes, pools, mud, or old
waterways are common.

COMMAND:
  setenemy amphibian

=============================================================================
